Employment at Daktronics

What is it like to work at Daktronics?Daktronics is the technical and innovation leader in our industry. We recruit smart, hardworking employees to deliver outstanding products and services to our growing markets. Employees from across the company share their thoughts on what makes Daktronics culture unique and why they love their jobs.Want to learn more about our employment opportunities? Check out our current open positions. We are an equal opportunity employer.
Search Open Jobs


    
Opportunities at Daktronics
 

StudentsStudents tell us they love the flexibility and pay!  Daktronics’ student employment program offers opportunity for a resume-building experience since most students work in an area that relates to their major. 


More About Students
 



InternshipsAn internship is an advantage for students entering the workplace, but a Daktronics Internship is an experience that is a step above the rest! Daktronics interns work full-time from January – August or May – December.


More About Interns
 



CareersJoin us, and see why Daktronics is the leader in our industry. We offer competitive compensation and benefits, in addition to meaningful and interesting work. Our people make the difference, every day.
