Sioux Falls Special Events


 
Brookings - Bring Your DreamsEnjoy a short commute, low crime rate, career opportunities, and a high quality of life in scenic Brookings, SD. Ranked 5th Best Small Town in America in 2013 by Livability, Brookings boasts an abundance of amenities and services. Whether you attend a sporting event at South Dakota State University (Go Jacks!) or the Brookings Summer Arts Festival, you won’t be disappointed in the recreational activities this vibrant community offers.


Learn More About Brookings 





















